page.title: 14BUS TIMETABLES
page.content: The first bus goes from Arncott Post Office every Monday to Friday at 7:00a.m. in the morning.It arrives in Oxford at 7:47a.m.The last bus from Charlton is at 5:30p.m. It returns from Oxford at 6:10p.m. On Monday the bus takes the school children to Bicester Swimming Pool at 1:15p.m. in the afternoon.We come back at 3:00p.m. Every day a bus comes to school to pick up children to go to Murcott and Fencott,and they get there at 3:10p.m. In the morning the bus comes to fetch them from Fencott and Murcott. It gets there at 8.45 a.m. The coaches sometimes take people to Blackpool in the holidays when they hire the coach. This year coaches were hired to take people to Ascot and some coaches go abroad.
